Summer rotation in RACI had a lunch meeting with Rudi and Vladi from RAC and I also met with Ted Murphy They are supposed to get back with me by Friday to confirm the proposed summer rotation So far I have a very positive impression of the group and the projects that they are involved in They also told me that RAC and Research people are often working on projects together so I am sure that my ties with Research are not going to go away with me rotating to RAC I will keep you posted on further developments Coordially Jason Sokolov

Summer rotation in RACI had a lunch meeting with Rudi and Vladi from RAC and I also met with Ted Murphy They are supposed to get back with me by Friday to confirm the proposed summer rotation So far I have a very positive impression of the group and the projects that they are involved in They also told me that RAC and Research people are often working on projects together so I am sure that my ties with Research are not going to go away with me rotating to RAC I will keep you posted on further developments Coordially Jason Sokolov

Resume of a nd year Rice MBA Chris NealeVince I talked to Chris last week during a recruiting event that Analyst and Associate pool hosted at Rice He was very interested in the kinds of projects that our group is working on Also he has had an extensive experience in the Energy industry I am attaching his resume He has one more year left in school but If you are interested I could invite him over to talk to our group members and get a better feel for the Enron Research environment Jason Original Message From nealer mailto Sent Saturday September PM To Sokolov Jason Subject Discussions Jason I enjoyed our discussions last Thursdaymuch more interesting that the usual partioMBA schmooze stuff I would very much like to talk to your Director about opportunities at Enron To be honest I am approaching Enron from several different points in order to pinpoint the area that best suits my abilities and sense of direction kind of mirroring the internal process that you would use to move between groups within Enron As Enron is the only large corporation that I am seriously considering talks with people such as yourself are invaluable in helping me find areas of commonality between the companys and my own goals Makes for a realistic set of expectations on both sides My resume is attached in Word format but sending emails from home via the Rice server sometimes buggers the attachments If you cant open the document let me know and I will send another copy both from my Roadrunner address as well as directly from school Thanks for the help Chris Neale Jones Graduate School of Management MBA Candidate Class of
